      "value": "<p>Your ability to overcome adversity is inspiring to your allies.</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> If you are affected by an effect that grants a negative penalty or miss chance to attack rolls and successfully hit the source of the effect with an attack, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to grant allies within 60 feet that are able to hear or see you a +1 morale bonus to attack and damage rolls against that enemy until the beginning of your next turn. If your attack was a critical hit, increase the morale bonus by 1.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.effects.Item.uGxeYfMidHEIqShC]{Effect: Epic Retort (Combat) +1}@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.effects.Item.6EvEBwwSRlAZgyCb]{Effect: Epic Retort (Combat) +2}</p>"
